    <h1 style="padding: 10px; font-size: 75px; color: black; border: solid; border-color: black; background-color: lightblue;"> 4 Star Characters</h1>
    <div class="left"><div class="item1">
   This is Beidou. Beidou is a really good electro character. Her skill is called Tidecaller, it's a counter, she take hits and is able to reflect them back for tons of damage if you do it at the correct time. Her burst (ultimate) is called storm breaker. Everytime u hit an enemy it will send out discharges of lightning jumping around dealing a good amount of damage. 
    <p></p>
