  <div class="left"><div class="item2"></div>
This is chongyun. Chongyun is good for cryo characters because his skill (Spirit Blade: Chonghua's Layered Frost) makes your normal attacks do cryo damage, so if you have a cryo(ice) character and you pair them with chongyun everything they do would do cryo damage. He can be very strong if you build him correctly. His ultimate (Spirit Blade: Cloud-Parting Star) drops swords from the sky and does cryo damage. 
